name: Edit First Index of Inventory - Product Name
fullName: Edit First Index of Inventory - Product Name

steps.name: Given I open the login page
And I login with email and password
Given user go to Inventory page
Then user go to edit page
assert expected **'Ubah Produk '** to include **'Ubah Produk'**
Then inventory product name will successfully edited
